113
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:15,050
<b>Dark Aster: Thuyền Chiến Kree</b>


114
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:26,490
Chúng gọi ta là "khủng bố",

115
00:13:26,660 --> 00:13:29,760
